N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4626.1 - Proceedings respecting licenses issued pursuant to Games of Chance Licensing Law

State Regulations

Proceedings to fine, suspend or revoke a license issued
pursuant to the Games of Chance Licensing Law may be instituted either by the
clerk, department or the commission, on its own initiative or on complaint of
any person, including any public official or agency. Notes
